    <properties>
        <title>Prerequisites for using AstroGrid</title>
        <author email="enter">Your Name</author>
    </properties>
    <body>
                <section name="Required technologies">
                        <p>
                                <li>Java 1.4.1 or later (but NOT Java 1.5.x)
                                        <p>AstroGrid webservices, and the infrastructure required to run them, are implemented in Java.</p>

                                        <p>Download it here:<a href="http://java.sun.com/j2se/">Sun j2se page</a></p>
                                 </li>
                         <p>
                                <li>Jakarta Tomcat 5.0.19
                                        <p>Tomcat provides the container server in which AstroGrid's web services run.</p>

                                        <p>Download it here:<a href="http://www.astrogrid.org/maven/downloads/jakarta-tomcat-5.0.19.tar.gz">Jakarta Tomcat 5.0.19</a></p>
                                        <p><a href="http://wiki.astrogrid.org/bin/view/Deploy/DeployingTomcat">Simple installation instructions</a></p>
                                        <p><a href="http://jakarta.apache.org/tomcat/tomcat-5.0-doc/index.html">General documentation</a></p>
                                 </li>
                      </p>
                        </p>
                 </section>
         <section name="Other Prerequisites">
                        <p>
                                <li>Maven 1.0.2
                                        <p>Maven is used for building and deploying AstroGrid web services from source; if you are installing AstroGrid components by
                                                dropping pre-built WAR files into tomcat (the simplest option), you won't need it.</p>

                                        <p>Download it here:<a href="http://www.astrogrid.org/maven/downloads/maven-1.0.2.tar.gz">maven-1.0.2</a></p>
                                    <p><a href="http://wiki.astrogrid.org/bin/view/Deploy/DeployingMaven">Simple installation instructions</a></p>
                                        <p><a href="http://maven.apache.org/reference/index.html">General documentation</a></p>
                                 </li>
                        </p>

                </section>
    </body>
